text: Inírida may refer to: *Inírida, Guainía, the capital city and a municipality of the Guainía Department in Colombia *Inírida River, a major tributary of the Guaviare River in the Guainía Department in Colombia *Inírida flower, an endemic plant in Colombia, scientific names Schoenocephalium teretifolium and Guacamaya superba
title: Inírida
